# App DataTable integration

Skill: `packages/flowtrove/src/components/datatable/.cursor/skills/implement-datatable-frontend/SKILL.md`

## Server list (default)

1. `get*Columns()` + `get*List(params: unknown)` in `api/index.ts`
2. `useBackendColumns` → `columnVisibility` → `DataTable` `initialState`
3. `fetch: (params) => getList(params)` — pass params unchanged
4. `queryKey: (params) => [PAGE_KEY, "list", params]`

Copy: `apps/app/src/pages/cadmin/pages/resources/pages/list/`

## Advanced (see advanced-server.md)

- Custom fetch / pagination mapping → secretary `student1`
- `fetchColumns(filters)` → filterBy columns
- Store actions → users list
- `actionBar` + `enableRowSelection` → orgunits/users
- Stats: separate `useQuery`, not inside DataTable

## Client (dialogs, small data)

```tsx
<DataTable disableParamPersistence source={{ type: "client", data: rows }} />
```

See `advanced-client.md`. No list API; optional columns API only.

## Backend

Go handlers required for server mode: `backends/packages/datatable/.cursor/skills/implement-datatable/`
